    "We draw attention to a singularity, (i) (Kumar et al. 2014) examined the pre-/post-treatment quality of life (QoL) in CxCa patients, (ii) (Zhang and Han 2020) investigated an under-researched cancer patient population, which is pregnant or lactating women, and (iii) (Asaduzzaman et al. 2021) implicated patients suffering from ovarian or cervical cancer, with stress (Mental) disorder too.",
